&lt;h2 id=&#34;frameworks&#34;&gt;Frameworks&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PeyrSharp is designed to be a modern library, therefore, we decided to ditch support for .NET Framework and .NET Core in favor of .NET 5, 6 and 7.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note: .NET Framework and .NET Core are not targeted by PeyrSharp, since they are no longer supported.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
